<h1 style="margin:0 0 8px; font-size:22px; font-weight:600; color:#17161a; letter-spacing:-0.3px;">
  Your password was changed
</h1>
<p style="margin:0 0 24px; font-size:15px; line-height:1.6; color:#5b5a5f;">
  The password for <strong style="color:#17161a;"><%= @resource.email %></strong> was just updated.
</p>

<table role="presentation" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="100%" style="background:#f6f5f1; border:1px solid #d9d7cf; border-radius:10px; margin:0 0 24px;">
  <tr>
    <td style="padding:18px 20px; font-size:13px; line-height:1.6; color:#5b5a5f;">
      If this was you, no action is needed. If you didn't change your password, reset it immediately and contact your organization's administrator.
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>
